,"tid":558210,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:50:48.000Z","msg":"辯方續指，專家證人證實涉案的麻蠅科蟲（又稱肉蠅）屬於「卵胎生」<br />\n我諗唔係法官冇bio知識<br />\n而係要聽個專定講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要考慮埋個可能性（專家話有）<br />\n<br />\n唔知個專家有d咩利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc353c13c1af660b828185c02936cfdfba745fa","tid":558210,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78aede27b8bc877c054362f9783622ebd56be6cd","tid":558210,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:50:48.000Z","msg":"辯方續指，專家證人證實涉案的麻蠅科蟲（又稱肉蠅）屬於「卵胎生」<br />\n我諗唔係法官冇bio知識<br />\n而係要聽個專定講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要考慮埋個可能性（專家話有）<br />\n<br />\n唔知個專家有d咩利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:52:26.000Z","msg":"辯方梗係搵個對自己有利既專家<br />\n<br />\n但呢D case 對大財團, 控方好明顯放軟手腳"},{"pid":"fb4810b29bd6c15427966aafa19aa163fbfd61e2","tid":558210,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:54:30.000Z","msg":"加上控方未有對店員證供作盤問挑戰，兩者分歧「足以對（事主）證供可信性蒙上嚴重疑問」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b215200a56ff9cf1ef0d75aba1d3a2ab5240c6dd","tid":558210,"uid":104298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T07:40:54.000Z","msg":"屌 諗起都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0882c1ae9f2fca4d547fc4c3e47b0c77ca91e1f0","tid":558210,"uid":12853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T07:43:59.000Z","msg":"鮮活抖動小蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好生動"},{"pid":"b745eb5fe20ee2e7b2e6749e7e1f433c208f8bcb","tid":558210,"uid":4917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T07:44:36.000Z","msg":"仆街，以後所有外賣全部無得告啦"},{"pid":"e540934d30dfa3663b38c359887c42b992b9ea1e","tid":558210,"uid